<BaseLayout
  title="The Story Behind Pinochle Pro: A Tribute to Bob and Shirley"
  description="The heartwarming story of Bob and Shirley Bearce — the real people behind Pinochle Pro's beloved characters."
  canonical="/history"
>
  <h1 class="title">The Story Behind Pinochle Pro</h1>

  <p>Years ago, amidst the excitement of Apple announcing the App Store for iOS and my ambition to develop my first game, I found inspiration in the spirited games of Pinochle played with my wife Sarah's family. Today, I want to share with you the heartwarming story behind this game, inspired by two incredible individuals: Bob and Shirley Bearce.</p>

  <p>It all began during visits to Sarah's grandparents, Bob and Shirley, at their retirement home in Mesa, Arizona. Whenever we gathered to play pinochle, it was a spectacle of laughter, bickering, and pure joy. Bob, a man of endless wit, had a knack for expressing his frustrations with the game in the most entertaining ways possible. He'd ask me, "What's the matter with you?" when he wouldn't get the card passed he needed. His colorful commentary and Shirley's witty retorts filled the room with life and laughter.</p>

  <p>Captivated by the charm of their banter, I started jotting down the funny remarks Bob would make during our games. Shirley, on the other hand, would merely grunt in disapproval at the sight of a misplay. Little did I know that these snippets of conversation would become the cornerstone of a project that would bring joy to countless people around the world.</p>

  <div class="section">
    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pinochle-pro/id567644839" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
