    <p class="caption">Pinochle Pro's Depiction of Bob &amp; Shirley</p>
    <p>In Pinochle Pro, players experience the fun of the game itself along with the dynamic interactions between animated characters. Their presence adds to the charm and nostalgia of the game.</p>
    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pinochle-pro/id567644839" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <img class="download-badge" src="https://developer.apple.com/app-store/marketing/guidelines/images/badge-download-on-the-app-store.svg" alt="Download on the App Store" />
    </a>
  </div>

  <p>Looking back, I am filled with gratitude for the inspiration that Bob and Shirley brought into my life. Their spirited banter, love of pinochle, and infectious humor continue to echo in the virtual world of Pinochle Pro. To this day, when we play in real life, family members say, "Grandma would be so disappointed" when they make a misplay. It is a reminder that even the simplest moments shared with loved ones can spark creativity and joy beyond measure.</p>

  <div class="section">
    <img src="/Bob&Shirley.jpg" alt="Bob and Shirley Bearce in 2009" class="photo" />
    <p class="caption">Bob and Shirley (2009)</p>
    <p>Bob and Shirley, unfortunately, passed away, but this game serves as a way to remember and honor them. Their spirit lives on in the joy and laughter that Pinochle Pro brings to players around the world.</p>
